title: Slow cooker peach upside-down cake
ingredients: ['3 (400g) tins sliced peaches in syrup, drained well', '70g butter, melted', '145g soft brown sugar', '1 teaspoon cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon nutmeg', '350g butter, softened', '200g caster sugar', '2 large eggs', '1/2 teaspoon almond extract', '250g plain flour', '2 teaspoons baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '240ml whole milk']
